commits.message:
use _.mergeWith instead of _.merge with customizer

It appears that the behavior of _.merge was changed in lodash 4, dropping support for a customizer function. This uses the new _.mergeWith in places where a customizer functionw as supplied.

pull_request.title: Fix scope docs
pull_request.body: It looks like the `grant_id` segment was omitted in the resource format description, even though it was present in the matrix. This adds it.
